title: NBA, Raptors, Kevin Durant, MVP, and the Warriors
itunes:title: NBA, Raptors, Kevin Durant, MVP, and the Warriors
description:
Colin defends the NBA, compares the Toronto Raptors to the 2010-11 Dallas Mavericks, breaks down Golden State Warriors F Kevin Durant's mobility, why Milwaukee Bucks F Giannis Antetokounmpo should be the MVP, and where he would rank the Warriors if they win another title. Guests include Chris Broussard, Mark Medina, Dan Woike, and Doug Gottlieb.
